snippet.title: Pathfinder Kingmaker Special Edition Unboxing (PC) ENGLISH
snippet.description:
Pathfinder: Kingmaker

Developer: Owlcat Games
Release Year: 2018
Genre: RPG
Platform: PC
Edition: EU Special

store.steampowered.com: Explore the Stolen Lands, a region that has been contested territory for centuries. Hundreds of kingdoms have risen and fallen in these lands, and now it is time for you to make your mark—by building your own kingdom! To do so, you’ll need to survive the harsh wilderness and the threat of rival nations… as well as threats within your own court.
